You arrive at a place that already has some tents set up and seems uninhabited.

In the distance you can see a large tower with stairs, as you stare up you can see that there are more ruins floating in the sky and that the only way to reach them is through that tower.

Undoubtedly, that tower is the place you need to go.
DescriptionAction: This may be a good place to rest before continuing.
